{"title":"Litespeed Flint is USA-Made Complete Ti Gravel Bike Under $3500","link":"https://bikerumor.com/litespeed-flint-usa-made-complete-ti-gravel-bike/","date":1692196105000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1276\" height=\"741\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-outside-feature-e1692115460298.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint outside feature\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-outside-feature-e1692115460298.jpeg 1276w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-outside-feature-e1692115460298-297x172.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-outside-feature-e1692115460298-800x465.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-outside-feature-e1692115460298-120x70.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-outside-feature-e1692115460298-768x446.jpeg 768w\" /></p>\n<p>Well, this is a great piece of news to report. <a href=\"https://litespeed.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Titanium bike manufacturer</a> Litespeed, just announced their new Flint titanium <a href=\"https://litespeed.com/products/flint\" target=\"_blank\">gravel bike</a> for $3395. The Flint is made right in their Chatanooga, Tennessee facility. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be clear, that price is not for just a frameset, it’s the price of a complete titanium gravel bike built up with Shimano GRX 600 components. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s get into the details. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint pedaling\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-pedaling.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Litespeed</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint on the move outside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-on-the-move-outside.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Calling the Flint “the sharpest blade in your quiver”, Litespeed says this bike is ready for anything. Whether riding off-road with buddies, race adventures, or bikebacking the Flint is a versatile bike offered in a very economical package. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint braceless seat stay\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-braceless-seat-stay.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint chainstay\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-chainstay.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Featuring a full 3AL/2.5V frame, the Flint is fabricated in their facility in Tennessee. It sports elegant, braceless seat stays allowing for full mud-shedding clearance, clean cable routing, and tire clearance for up to a 48mm tire. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-logo-e1692117647298.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"377\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-logo-e1692117647298-800x377.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint anodized logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-logo-e1692117647298-800x377.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-logo-e1692117647298-297x140.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-logo-e1692117647298-120x57.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-logo-e1692117647298-768x362.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-logo-e1692117647298.jpeg 1276w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Frame is also equipped with all of the mounts you might need, for fenders, nutrition, racks, and hydration/storage. Litespeed says that no matter how you pack it down, the Flint stays “stable without sacrificing agility, and moves with ease where you want – when you want”. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint headtube top tube down tube junction\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-top-tube-down-tube-junction.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-down-tube-logo.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"542\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-down-tube-logo-800x542.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint anodized down tube logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-down-tube-logo-800x542.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-down-tube-logo-297x201.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-down-tube-logo-120x81.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-down-tube-logo-768x520.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-anodized-down-tube-logo.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can pick your style as well when ordering the Flint. You can pick from a wide selection of vinyl graphics or even consider etched graphics or ToDize color anodizing upgrade. The choice is yours.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Litespeed Retail and Build Options</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint dropped drive side chain stay\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-dropped-drive-side-chain-stay.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint frame shot with fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-frame-shot-with-fork.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Litespeed Flint is fully customizable when it comes to ordering your own bike. There are many, many options to choose from for drivetrains, 8 to be exact. So, I will keep it simple and pick the popular ones and list them below. Please <a href=\"https://litespeed.com/products/flint\" target=\"_blank\">check here</a> for all of the many different combos you can choose from, go nuts…</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>$3395 (Shimano GRX 600 1x build)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>$3895 (Shimano GRX 810 1x build)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>$4645 (Shimano GRX 810 Di2 1x build)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>$4895 (SRAM Force XPLR AXS D2 1x build)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>$2095 (frame and seat collar only)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Litespeed Flint Key Features</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint Frameset Dropped Chainstay\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-Frameset-Dropped-Chainstay.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint headbadge\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headbadge.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"523\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-800x523.jpeg\" alt=\"Litespeed Flint headtube\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-800x523.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-297x194.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-120x78.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube-768x502.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-headtube.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>A full 3AL/2.5V frame with frame size-specific tube sets, that are all wall-thickness controlled in-house for consistency and feature zero aluminum inserts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>In-house designed and CNC-machined titanium dropouts, disc brake mount, headtube and bottom bracket for optimized strength-to-weight</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tire clearance to 48mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A dropped drive-side chainstay for improved chainring and tire clearance</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A UDH rear derailleur hanger</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bosses for three bottles (downtube, seat tube, and downtube underside)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Geometry with a slightly elongated wheelbase and adjusted stack/reach measure that deliver stability and performance to riders from weekend trail riders to competitive gravel riders</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Boundless options for upgrades, from components and bottom bracket standard to vinyl graphic, etching, or color anodizing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Flint marks the debut of the new Chameleon blue/green fade color anodizing upgrade option</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fast lead time, shipping two to three weeks from the date of order</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Litespeed-Flint-hero-front-side-e1692117956115.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy